QuestData.Title: Just Checkin'
QuestData.Description: There have been fearsome sounds echoing from Gundrak. They have been increasing in volume and frequency of late.$b$bMy long-time student is currently recording events from inside Gundrak. Perhaps you could find the time to check in on her for me?
QuestData.LogDescription: To'kini wants you to speak to Bah'kini in Gundrak.
